{"tid":640084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港移民36年前被殺 澳懸紅600萬緝兇","createTime":"2018-04-24T04:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T11:51:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2f06bcd549384f17346f5213c340091384c3a502","tid":640084,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T04:15:47.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】澳洲維多利亞省警方懸紅一百萬澳元（六百萬港元），偵緝三十六年前即一九八二年，墨爾本華裔女子、香港移民吳珍妮（Jenny Rose Ng，音譯）被殺案的兇手。<br />\n<br />\n一九八二年，已經與丈夫分開的三十九歲女子吳珍妮和四名子女、父母，同住在墨爾本東區基尤（Kew）。案發於四月二十三日，早上八時半，她的七歲和九歲女兒、十一歲兒子看過母親在生時的最後一面後，離家上課。過了約四小時，兩名女兒放學回家吃午飯，卻發現母親的屍體。吳女被兇徒斬了三十刀，十一個月大的小女兒坐在隔壁房間的嬰兒牀上，但沒有受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n警察調查後發現一名男子在當天早上約十時半進入吳女的寓所，但男子身分一直成謎。周一是吳女死忌三十六周年，維省警方懸紅一百萬澳元追尋兇手。根據新的調查，警方相信吳女認識兇手，並開門讓其進入寓所。證人供述，當天早上約十時半，聽到有男子敲吳女在十九樓公寓的門，接着聽到吳女用粵語應門，後來聽到公寓傳出噪音，仿佛有人在移動家具或大力撞門，不久，噪音就停止了。吳女與丈夫吳侃河(音譯，Kam Hor Ng)一九六九年在香港結婚，但婚後不和睦，在吳女懷着小女兒時兩人分開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7__db0x1lv1LseZZJl0yQQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDI1O2g9MjgzO2lsPXBsYW5l/https://media.zenfs.com/creatr-images/GLB/2018-04-23/cac07550-474b-11e8-b4f7-0be4cd3d427e_i_425x283_003114212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7__db0x1lv1LseZZJl0yQQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NDI1O2g9MjgzO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fcreatr-images%2FGLB%2F2018-04-23%2Fcac07550-474b-11e8-b4f7-0be4cd3d427e_i_425x283_003114212.jpg&h=ec8b2704&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%9136%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA-%E6%BE%B3%E6%87%B8%E7%B4%85600%E8%90%AC%E7%B7%9D%E5%85%87-221118219.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%259136%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%2587%25B8%25E7%25B4%2585600%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%25B7%259D%25E5%2585%2587-221118219.html&d=vtPIsuv%2BIxLerqTTrvhoOghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=f824fc3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%9136%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA-%E6%BE%B3%E6%87%B8%E7%B4%85600%E8%90%AC%E7%B7%9D%E5%85%87-221118219.html</a>"},{"pid":"1c4266709b6480aeeb60d1b3049e73344c8820c7","tid":640084,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:41:09.000Z","msg":"推post"},{"pid":"980a18e4c27e5beb6c0ed90e264468f99b261d83","tid":640084,"uid":180258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:42:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cea18102b94f2d5f71e121738ad5fec654ab94ec","tid":640084,"uid":143131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"連登眾神探速速歸位"},{"pid":"ffc3664d500b7dbc3e4bf36c7cca170917fb0aa7","tid":640084,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"Cold Case 重開應該夠料差廚了"},{"pid":"832e504d41a2f5faba8b4dfa778c213953ec646a","tid":640084,"uid":57329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"三十六年後先懸紅?<br />\n點查 除非留低關鍵科學証據<br />\n但有嘅話都唔駛懸紅"},{"pid":"0544d0cfa0f00e3b2fca6b47977e4dcb6007282e","tid":640084,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"點解咁耐先翻案"},{"pid":"7bce5f816b4305be130e299a88882652c73a9883","tid":640084,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:02:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a588b530e75b7548645f16bc2c8c8599977ff8fc","tid":640084,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0544d0cfa0f00e3b2fca6b47977e4dcb6007282e","tid":640084,"uid":41846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"點解咁耐先翻案"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:28:32.000Z","msg":"應該有新線索"},{"pid":"042e577c9879dd4c0605c652045c5ebf17893cff","tid":640084,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":